{"tid":1042330,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如果徐志摩係呢個時代出世 會唔會俾人屌話佢偽文青MK仔","createTime":"2019-03-01T13:11:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T18:09:54.000Z","uid":137707,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d044e7b7d2b715b66dc98b7a50d903c7c61f26a2","tid":1042330,"uid":137707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T13:11:57.000Z","msg":"「愛情是一個人加上另一個人，可是，一加一卻不等於二，就像你加上我，也並不等於我們。」<br />\n<br />\n「習慣，睡伴，習慣一個人在一個房間，抱著絨絨熊，獨眠。習慣，吃鹹，習慣傷口的那把鹽，在我心裏一點點蔓延。」<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解覺得好似而家啲文青會寫／會講嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果佢係呢個時代出世 應該會俾人cap ig 公審（一腳踏幾船）同笑柒佢寫嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ffa60a4692ac4c94378efb0f4ff79068bea8d4","tid":1042330,"uid":239954,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T13:14:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"384887c2a41bdd8e2effb02801f2496226cb0dcf","tid":1042330,"uid":137707,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"c7ffa60a4692ac4c94378efb0f4ff79068bea8d4","tid":1042330,"uid":239954,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T13:14:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T13:16:59.000Z","msg":"有才華就叫多情才子<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係感情方面 我都覺得佢係一個仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90c9f0340b9f26ab270dcfa4ffbf828951901e77","tid":1042330,"uid":126309,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T13:18:26.000Z","msg":"搵佢做填詞人"},{"pid":"5801cfc25a2fb601fe7a2e923a992d87ef902e89","tid":1042330,"uid":9231,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T13:21:33.000Z","msg":"謙謙出生係佢果個時代會成為一代傳奇"},{"pid":"5d30b3918411cd4fac95e2ecc27ea18693ce7170","tid":1042330,"uid":137707,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5801cfc25a2fb601fe7a2e923a992d87ef902e89","tid":1042330,"